```r
mOTU <- readRDS(\../data/R/mOTU.rds\) %>%
  filter_taxa(sum(abun) != 0)
amr <- readRDS(\../data/R/amr.rds\) %>%
  filter_taxa(sum(abun) != 0)
```

<!-- rnb-source-begin eyJkYXRhIjoiYGBgclxubU9UVSA8LSBtT1RVICU+JVxuICBtdXRhdGVfdGF4YShcbiAgICBtX3ByZXZhbGVuY2UgPSBzdW0oYWJ1bj4wKSAgLyBsZW5ndGgoYWJ1biksXG4gICAgbV9sb2cxMF9zdW1fdGF4YSA9IGxvZzEwKHN1bShhYnVuKSksXG4gICAgbV9sb2cxMF9tYXhfcmVsID0gbG9nMTAobWF4KHJlbGEpKSxcbiAgICBtX2xvZzEwX21lYW5fbm9femVybyA9IGxvZzEwKG1lYW4oYWJ1blthYnVuPjBdKSksXG4gICAgbV9sb2cxMF9tZWRpYW5fbm9femVybyA9IGxvZzEwKG1lZGlhbihhYnVuW2FidW4+MF0pKSlcbmBgYCJ9 -->

```r
mOTU <- mOTU %>%
  mutate_taxa(
    m_prevalence = sum(abun>0)  / length(abun),
    m_log10_sum_taxa = log10(sum(abun)),
    m_log10_max_rel = log10(max(rela)),
    m_log10_mean_no_zero = log10(mean(abun[abun>0])),
    m_log10_median_no_zero = log10(median(abun[abun>0])))

<!-- rnb-source-begin eyJkYXRhIjoiYGBgclxubU9UVSAlPiVcbiAgZ2F0aGVyX3RheGEoKSAlPiVcbiAgc2VsZWN0KHRheGFfaWQsIHN0YXJ0c193aXRoKFwibV9cIikpICU+JVxuICBwaXZvdF9sb25nZXIoLXRheGFfaWQsIG5hbWVzX3RvID0gXCJtZWFzdXJtZW50c1wiLCB2YWx1ZXNfdG8gPSBcInZhbHVlc1wiKSAlPiVcbiAgZ2dwbG90KGFlcyh4ID0gdmFsdWVzKSkgK1xuICBnZW9tX2hpc3RvZ3JhbShiaW5zID0gMzAsIGZpbGwgPSBcImxpZ2h0Ymx1ZVwiLCBjb2xvciA9IFwiZGFya2JsdWVcIikgK1xuICBmYWNldF93cmFwKH5tZWFzdXJtZW50cywgc2NhbGVzID0gXCJmcmVlXCIsIG5jb2wgPSAzKSArXG4gIHRoZW1lX2J3KClcbmBgYCJ9 -->

```r
mOTU %>%
  gather_taxa() %>%
  select(taxa_id, starts_with(\m_\)) %>%
  pivot_longer(-taxa_id, names_to = \measurments\, values_to = \values\) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = values)) +
  geom_histogram(bins = 30, fill = \lightblue\, color = \darkblue\) +
  facet_wrap(~measurments, scales = \free\, ncol = 3) +
  theme_bw()
```

<!-- rnb-source-end -->
```r
mOTU %>%
  gather_taxa() %>%
  select(taxa_id, starts_with(\m_\)) %>%
  pivot_longer(-taxa_id, names_to = \measurments\, values_to = \values\) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = values)) +
  geom_histogram(bins = 30, fill = \lightblue\, color = \darkblue\) +
  facet_wrap(~measurments, scales = \free\, ncol = 3) +
  theme_bw()

mOTU_filt <- mOTU %>%
  mutate_meta(sample_sum = sum(abun)) %>%
  filter_taxa(m_prevalence >= .25 & m_log10_median_no_zero >= 0) %>%
  mutate_meta(preserved_counts = sum(abun) / sample_sum)

mOTU_filt <- mOTU %>%
  mutate_meta(sample_sum = sum(abun)) %>%
  filter_taxa(m_prevalence >= .25 & m_log10_median_no_zero >= 0) %>%
  mutate_meta(preserved_counts = sum(abun) / sample_sum)

  gather_meta() %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = preserved_counts)) +

amr_filt <- amr_filt %>%
  mutate_taxa(
    m_prevalence = sum(abun>0) / length(abun),
    m_log10_sum_taxa = log10(sum(abun)),
    m_log10_max_rel = log10(max(rela)),
    m_log10_mean_no_zero = log10(mean(abun[abun>0])),
    m_log10_median_no_zero = log10(median(abun[abun>0]))) 



<!-- rnb-output-end -->

amr_filt %>%
  gather_taxa() %>%
  select(taxa_id, starts_with(\m_\)) %>%
  pivot_longer(-taxa_id, names_to = \measurments\, values_to = \values\) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = values)) +
  geom_histogram(bins = 30, fill = \lightblue\, color = \darkblue\) +
  facet_wrap(~measurments, scales = \free\, ncol = 3) +
  theme_bw()

amr_filt <- amr_filt %>%
  filter_taxa(m_prevalence >= .25 & m_log10_median_no_zero >= -2) %>%
  mutate_meta(preserved_counts = sum(abun) / sample_sum)

amr_filt <- amr_filt %>%
  filter_taxa(m_prevalence >= .25 & m_log10_median_no_zero >= -2) %>%
  mutate_meta(preserved_counts = sum(abun) / sample_sum)

  gather_meta() %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = preserved_counts)) +
  geom_histogram(bins = 30, fill = \lightblue\, color = \darkblue\) +

## Construct the network mOTU + amr (all acquired and functional)


<!-- rnb-text-end -->


<!-- rnb-chunk-begin -->


<!-- rnb-output-begin eyJkYXRhIjoiXG48IS0tIHJuYi1zb3VyY2UtYmVnaW4gZXlKa1lYUmhJam9pWUdCZ2NseHViVTlVVlY5aGJYSmZibVYwZHlBOExTQnRaMjVsZENoY2JpQWdibTl5YlNBOUlHTmlhVzVrS0c1dmNtMG9iVTlVVlY5bWFXeDBLU3dnYm05eWJTaGhiWEpmWm1sc2RDa3BMRnh1SUNCdFpYUmhJRDBnYldWMFlTaHRUMVJWWDJacGJIUXBJQ1UrSlNCelpXeGxZM1FvTFhCeVpYTmxjblpsWkY5amIzVnVkSE1wTEZ4dUlDQjBZWGhoSUQwZ1ltbHVaRjl5YjNkektIUmhlR0VvYlU5VVZWOW1hV3gwS1N3Z2RHRjRZU2hoYlhKZlptbHNkQ2twWEc0cFhHNWdZR0FpZlE9PSAtLT5cblxuYGBgclxubU9UVV9hbXJfbmV0dyA8LSBtZ25ldChcbiAgbm9ybSA9IGNiaW5kKG5vcm0obU9UVV9maWx0KSwgbm9ybShhbXJfZmlsdCkpLFxuICBtZXRhID0gbWV0YShtT1RVX2ZpbHQpICU+JSBzZWxlY3QoLXByZXNlcnZlZF9jb3VudHMpLFxuICB0YXhhID0gYmluZF9yb3dzKHRheGEobU9UVV9maWx0KSwgdGF4YShhbXJfZmlsdCkpXG4pXG5gYGBcblxuPCEtLSBybmItc291cmNlLWVuZCAtLT5cbiJ9 -->

mOTU_amr_netw <- mgnet(
  norm = cbind(norm(mOTU_filt), norm(amr_filt)),
  meta = meta(mOTU_filt) %>% select(-preserved_counts),
  taxa = bind_rows(taxa(mOTU_filt), taxa(amr_filt))
)



<!-- rnb-output-end -->

<!-- rnb-output-begin eyJkYXRhIjoiXG48IS0tIHJuYi1zb3VyY2UtYmVnaW4gZXlKa1lYUmhJam9pWUdCZ2NseHVZR0JnY2x4dWJVOVVWVjloYlhKZmJtVjBkeUE4TFNCdFoyNWxkQ2hjYmlBZ2JtOXliU0E5SUdOaWFXNWtLRzV2Y20wb2JVOVVWVjltYVd4MEtTd2dibTl5YlNoaGJYSmZabWxzZENrcExGeHVJQ0J0WlhSaElEMGdiV1YwWVNodFQxUlZYMlpwYkhRcElDVStKU0J6Wld4bFkzUW9MWEJ5WlhObGNuWmxaRjlqYjNWdWRITXBMRnh1SUNCMFlYaGhJRDBnWW1sdVpGOXliM2R6S0hSaGVHRW9iVTlVVlY5bWFXeDBLU3dnZEdGNFlTaGhiWEpmWm1sc2RDa3BYRzRwWEc1Z1lHQmNibUJnWUNKOSAtLT5cblxuYGBgclxuYGBgclxubU9UVV9hbXJfbmV0dyA8LSBtZ25ldChcbiAgbm9ybSA9IGNiaW5kKG5vcm0obU9UVV9maWx0KSwgbm9ybShhbXJfZmlsdCkpLFxuICBtZXRhID0gbWV0YShtT1RVX2ZpbHQpICU+JSBzZWxlY3QoLXByZXNlcnZlZF9jb3VudHMpLFxuICB0YXhhID0gYmluZF9yb3dzKHRheGEobU9UVV9maWx0KSwgdGF4YShhbXJfZmlsdCkpXG4pXG5gYGBcbmBgYFxuXG48IS0tIHJuYi1zb3VyY2UtZW5kIC0tPlxuIn0= -->

spearman_mat <- cor(norm(mOTU_amr_netw), method = \spearman\) %>%
  as_tibble(rownames = \taxa_i\) %>%
  pivot_longer(-taxa_i, names_to = \taxa_j\, values_to = \spearman\) %>%
  filter(taxa_i > taxa_j)

p_depth_amr <- amr %>%
  mutate_meta(sample_sum = sum(abun)) %>%
  gather_meta() %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = sample_sum)) +
  geom_histogram(bins = 30, fill = \lightblue\, color = \darkblue\) +
  theme_bw() +
  theme(legend.position = \right\) +
  scale_x_log10() +
  xlab(\AMR Sample Depth\) +
  geom_vline(xintercept = 15, color = \red\, linewidth = 2)
p_depth_amr

p_bar_sample_removed <- mOTU %>%
  gather_meta() %>%
  filter(!sample_id %in% preserved_samples) %>%
  group_by(Region, country_alt) %>%
  summarise(n = n(), .groups = \drop\) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = country_alt, y = n, fill = Region)) +
  geom_bar(stat = \identity\) +
  theme_bw() +
  theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 45, hjust = 1, vjust = 1)) +
  theme(legend.position = \top\, axis.title.x = element_blank()) +
  ylab(\Sample Filtered\)
p_bar_sample_removed

```r
p_bar_sample_removed <- mOTU %>%
  gather_meta() %>%
  filter(!sample_id %in% preserved_samples) %>%
  group_by(Region, country_alt) %>%
  summarise(n = n(), .groups = \drop\) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x = country_alt, y = n, fill = Region)) +
  geom_bar(stat = \identity\) +
  theme_bw() +
  theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 45, hjust = 1, vjust = 1)) +
  theme(legend.position = \top\, axis.title.x = element_blank()) +
  ylab(\Sample Filtered\)
p_bar_sample_removed
```
